@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content="Bounce n Bang is a free physics puzzle game: aim your cannon, ricochet cannonballs off walls, beat bosses, and climb the global leaderboard. Medieval adventure, 60+ levels, family-friendly." />
    <title>Bounce n Bang — Physics puzzle game | ShahKing Games</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, sans-serif;
            --accent: #e94560;
            --accent-hover: #ff6b6b;
            --muted: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.85);
            --dim: rgba(238, 238, 238, 0.75);
        }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            background: #1a1a2e;
            color: #eee;
        }
        main {
            padding: 2rem 1.25rem 2.5rem;
            max-width: 40rem;
        }
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }
        h1 {
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .tagline {
            opacity: 0.92;
            line-height: 1.55;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }
        .video-wrap {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .video-title {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 0.65rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .video-embed {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            padding-bottom: 56.25%;
            height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: #000;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }
        .video-embed iframe {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: 0;
        }
        .about {
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .about h2 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .about h3 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 650;
            margin: 1.35rem 0 0.45rem;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .about p {
            margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
            line-height: 1.65;
            color: var(--dim);
            font-size: 0.98rem;
        }
        .about ul {
            margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
            padding-left: 1.25rem;
            line-height: 1.55;
            color: var(--dim);
        }
        .about li {
            margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
        }
        .about .closing {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding-top: 1rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--muted);
        }
        .links {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.85rem;
            align-items: stretch;
        }
        .links a {
            display: block;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background 0.15s ease;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .links a:hover,
        .links a:focus-visible {
            background: var(--accent-hover);
            outline: 2px solid #fff;
            outline-offset: 2px;
        }
        .links a.secondary {
            background: #16213e;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }
        .links a.secondary:hover,
        .links a.secondary:focus-visible {
            background: #0f3460;
        }
        .hint {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.45;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main>
        <header class="hero">
            <h1>Bounce n Bang</h1>
            <p class="tagline">A medieval physics puzzle where every shot is a ricochet—and every level is a new excuse to say “just one more try.”</p>
        </header>

        <section class="video-wrap" aria-labelledby="video-heading">
            <h2 id="video-heading" class="video-title">Watch the trailer</h2>
            <div class="video-embed">
                <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZpJnjLp14wA"
                        title="Bounce n Bang — trailer video"
                        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                        referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
                        allowfullscreen
                        loading="lazy"></iframe>
            </div>
        </section>

        <article class="about" id="about">
            <h2>About the game</h2>
            <p>
                <strong>Bounce n Bang: Physics Puzzler</strong> drops you into a cartoon-medieval world that’s equal parts brain-teaser and ballistics lab.
                You’re not just tapping—you’re lining up cannon shots, banking cannonballs off stone walls, threading shots past barriers, and watching the perfect ricochet wipe the smile off a castle full of troublemakers.
            </p>

            <h3>Aim, bounce, outsmart</h3>
            <p>
                Each stage is a small puzzle box: angles matter, patience pays off, and that “impossible” shot suddenly clicks when you see the bounce path.
                With <strong>60+ levels</strong> (and counting), there’s always a new layout to crack and a new trick to learn—whether you’re into casual puzzle games or you live for leaderboard bragging rights.
            </p>

            <h3>Boss fights that bite back</h3>
            <p>
                When ordinary targets aren’t enough, you’ll square off against bigger threats—including showdowns that feel straight out of a fantasy story.
                Quick thinking beats button mashing: read the room, adjust your aim, and turn a bad round into a comeback.
            </p>

            <h3>Upgrades &amp; global competition</h3>
            <p>
                Power up your cannon, experiment with how your shots feel, then take it online—climb the <strong>global leaderboards</strong> and see how your skills stack up against players around the world.
            </p>

            <h3>Free to play, fair choices</h3>
            <p>
                The full free puzzle experience is there without paying to progress.
                Prefer an uninterrupted session? Grab the <strong>premium</strong> option for an ad-free ride—totally optional.
            </p>

            <h3>At a glance</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Physics-based cannon puzzles—master the bounce, not just the tap</li>
                <li>60+ unique levels of ricochet mayhem</li>
                <li>Epic boss-style challenges (dragons and bigger surprises)</li>
                <li>Cannon upgrades and rewards that keep progression satisfying</li>
                <li>Strategic blockers and extras that reward clever play</li>
                <li>Leaderboards for competitive puzzle fans</li>
                <li>Easy to pick up, hard to put down—great for families who love brain games</li>
            </ul>

            <p>
                If you like <strong>bounce ball games</strong>, <strong>ricochet puzzles</strong>, or medieval adventure with a lighthearted tone, this one’s built for you.
                Every level is another chance to nail the shot that makes you grin before the dust even settles.
            </p>

            <p class="closing">
                We’re always polishing Bounce n Bang—reviews and feedback genuinely help us tune levels, balance, and fun.
                Grab it on Google Play, play a few stages, and tell us what you think.
            </p>
        </article>

        <nav class="links" aria-label="Game links">
            <a href="https://www.shahkings.com/bouncenbang/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Visit the Bounce n Bang page (ShahKing Games)</a>
            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.shah.BnB" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Download on Google Play (free)</a>
            <a class="secondary" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.shah.BounceBang" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bounce N Bang — Premium (ad-free)</a>
        </nav>
        <p class="hint">Store links open in a new tab.</p>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
